From 7e2615bb5ccce1d62e0db7d5b5f151b804e77b9c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Lorri Rao <zouyoo@outlook.com>
Date: Fri, 13 Mar 2026 22:38:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Cosmo development patches for Tensile tuning

Aggregated fixes from cosmo workspace:
- Fix TFLOPS reporting for grouped GEMM (sum all sub-gemms)
- Fix int32 overflow in rotating buffer size calculation
- Fix int32 overflow in rotating-buffer-size CLI arg parsing
- Add hipMalloc error handling in RotatingMemory
- Add hsaco filename alias for xnack-qualified targets
- Guard empty/invalid assembly in TensileCreateLibrary
- Replace glibc rand() with thread-local RNG to avoid lock contention
- Fix origami setup.py for editable install
